# Smart Tamper Detection System

## Overview
This project detects tampering in weighing and measuring instruments using IoT concepts.

## Features
- Real-time tamper detection
- Data logging
- API-based monitoring
- Simple dashboard integration

## Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express.js
- REST API

## API Endpoints

### GET /
Check server status

### POST /tamper
Send tamper data

Example:
{
  "deviceId": "Device1",
  "tamper": true,
  "location": "Pune"
}

### GET /tamper
Get all records

## Future Scope
- IoT sensor integration
- Blockchain logging
- AI-based anomaly detection
